00:06:19.830 --> 00:06:23.400
NARRATOR:
The Miss America Pageant started
out as a promotional gimmick

00:06:23.400 --> 00:06:27.930
dreamed up by Atlantic City
businessmen in 1921

00:06:27.930 --> 00:06:31.900
as a way to keep tourists
in town after Labor Day.

00:06:34.260 --> 00:06:36.160
Over the next eight decades,

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:38.730
it would become
a national tradition

00:06:38.730 --> 00:06:42.030
dedicated to defining
the ideal American woman.

00:06:42.030 --> 00:06:46.200
