00:08:16.730 --> 00:08:19.230
The only rule
for the competition

00:08:19.230 --> 00:08:21.730
was that all participants

00:08:21.730 --> 00:08:25.330
must positively be attired
in bathing costumes.

00:08:25.330 --> 00:08:27.900
A board of censors
had been appointed

00:08:27.900 --> 00:08:30.260
to review questionable entries.

00:08:30.260 --> 00:08:32.360
