00:30:40.530 --> 00:30:43.430
Now, we've just learned
all the details

00:30:43.430 --> 00:30:45.700
of six million Jews
being killed,

00:30:45.700 --> 00:30:48.860
slaughtered, burned, tortured.

00:30:48.860 --> 00:30:50.930
And naturally,
it attracts attention,

00:30:50.930 --> 00:30:55.000
and the juxtaposition of the
two things was so improbable.

00:30:55.000 --> 00:30:57.400
There were people
that would come to the hotel

00:30:57.400 --> 00:30:59.700
where I was staying
with my sister.

00:30:59.700 --> 00:31:02.130
They would introduce themselves
to me and say,

00:31:02.130 --> 00:31:05.230
"I'm Jewish,
and it's just wonderful

00:31:05.230 --> 00:31:07.000
that you're in this contest."

00:31:07.000 --> 00:31:08.930
But how about
when people came up to you

00:31:08.930 --> 00:31:11.560
