00:32:08.960 --> 00:32:11.900
a 21-year-old, 5'10" brunette,

00:32:11.900 --> 00:32:14.660
Bess Myerson,
Hunter College graduate.

00:32:16.860 --> 00:32:19.530
NARRATOR:
By the time
Myerson's name was announced,

00:32:19.530 --> 00:32:23.030
her sister, Sylvia,
was already in tears.

00:32:25.460 --> 00:32:27.660
From the audience came shouts
of<i> "Mazel tov!"</i>

00:32:29.730 --> 00:32:33.500
"Don't let anybody kid you,"
Myerson said years later.

00:32:33.500 --> 00:32:36.760
"It was one hell
of a terrific moment."

00:32:39.360 --> 00:32:44.830
LEVI:
Bess was the answer
