It was a symbol of a certain
statement against anti-Semitism.

00:32:51.530 --> 00:32:53.660
It was a symbol of a victory
against Hitler.

00:32:53.660 --> 00:32:55.200
It was a symbol for women,

00:32:55.200 --> 00:32:58.760
and when she won, there was
great celebration in our house.

00:32:58.760 --> 00:33:00.830
It was like when Roosevelt won
or something.

00:33:02.700 --> 00:33:05.830
NARRATOR:
Myerson expected to spend
her reign making appearances

00:33:05.830 --> 00:33:09.530
and promoting
the pageant's new sponsors.

00:33:09.530 --> 00:33:12.930
But after an obligatory
four-week performance tour,

00:33:12.930 --> 00:33:14.600
where drunks in the audience
demanded

00:33:14.600 --> 00:33:17.730
she play the piano
in her bathing suit,

00:33:17.730 --> 00:33:20.960
there were few requests
for her time.

00:33:20.960 --> 00:33:24.660
None of the sponsors wanted
a Jewish girl--

00:33:24.660 --> 00:33:26.600
even a Jewish Miss America--

00:33:26.600 --> 00:33:30.100
posing with their products.

00:33:30.100 --> 00:33:33.060
MYERSON:
Halfway through that year,
I said to the pageant,

00:33:33.060 --> 00:33:34.860
"I'm not available to you
anymore,

00:33:34.860 --> 00:33:36.860
"because I want to do
