00:34:18.530 --> 00:34:20.330
and a very different kind
of reign.

00:34:20.330 --> 00:34:25.300
NARRATOR:
Myerson had made Miss America
a scholar and a lady.

00:34:25.300 --> 00:34:29.100
But the following year,
pageant judges made it clear

00:34:29.100 --> 00:34:31.330
that looks still counted.

