"Yolande was the sexiest,
most glamorous thing

00:39:01.860 --> 00:39:04.930
I had ever laid eyes on,"
she later said.

00:39:06.330 --> 00:39:07.760
Slaughter's new husband,

00:39:07.760 --> 00:39:11.030
a business manager
for the pageant, agreed.

00:39:11.030 --> 00:39:13.430
"She can't lose," he predicted,

00:39:13.430 --> 00:39:15.830
"unless the women judges
run away from her."

00:39:20.960 --> 00:39:24.360
