The morning
after she was crowned,

00:40:09.000 --> 00:40:12.200
the new Miss America was
summoned to a breakfast meeting,

00:40:12.200 --> 00:40:14.000
where she was to be briefed
on her duties

00:40:14.000 --> 00:40:15.500
for the coming year.

00:40:17.460 --> 00:40:19.860
