I did not know
what to expect with this.

00:40:19.860 --> 00:40:21.630
So I arrived and they...

00:40:21.630 --> 00:40:25.230
All these, these suits
were sitting about.

00:40:25.230 --> 00:40:27.860
Older men, board of directors,
congratulated me,

00:40:27.860 --> 00:40:31.100
and said, "Now, Miss Betbeze,
this is what I represent.

00:40:31.100 --> 00:40:33.800
This is what you're going to do
for us."

00:40:33.800 --> 00:40:36.360
Then it came
to the bathing suit,

00:40:36.360 --> 00:40:38.500
the most important sponsor.

00:40:38.500 --> 00:40:42.260
And this man said to me, "In
November, we'll be in Wyoming,

00:40:42.260 --> 00:40:44.260
and you'll wear
this and that bathing suit."

00:40:44.260 --> 00:40:47.700
I said, "Wait a minute, please.

00:40:47.700 --> 00:40:50.000
"No-- no way.

00:40:50.000 --> 00:40:52.130
"Go into Milwaukee
